{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solve\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">solve</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">scope</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Scope\">Scope</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The main VC generation step. Operates on a plain `MVarId` with no knowledge of grind.\nReturns `.goals subgoals` when the goal was decomposed, or a classification result\n(`.noEntailment`, `.noProgramOrLatticeFoundInTarget`, etc.) when no further decomposition is\npossible.\n\nThe function performs the following steps in order:\n\n1. **Forall introduction**: If the target is a `∀`, simp it and introduce binders.\n2. **Target-let handling**: zeta-substitute duplicable top-level lets, otherwise introduce them.\n3. **Triple unfolding**: If the target is `⦃P⦄ x ⦃Q; E⦄`, unfold into `P ⊑ wp x Q E`.\n4. **Syntactic rfl**: close `pre ⊑ rhs` by `PartialOrder.rel_refl` when both sides unify.\n5. **Embedded pure precondition introduction**: lift a `⌜φ⌝` precondition into the local\n   context, before state-argument introduction would apply it to the introduced arguments.\n6. **State-argument introduction**: If the lattice carrier is a function type\n   `σ₁ → ... → σₙ → Base`, introduce all excess state arguments.\n7. **Bare pure precondition introduction**: on the `Prop` lattice, replace a `True`\n   precondition by `⊤` and lift any other precondition into the local context.\n8. **EPost projection reduction**: reduce an `EPost.Cons.head` RHS to the projected component.\n9. **Lattice decomposition**: decompose `⊓`, `⇨`, `⌜p⌝` and `⊤` RHS connectives.\n10. **Lifted-hypothesis discharge**: close a residual `pre ⊑ ⌜φ⌝` entailment against the most\n    recently lifted precondition `h : φ` in the local context, cached in `Scope.lastLiftedPre?`.\n11. **WP decomposition**: when the RHS is `wp e post epost s₁ ... sₙ`, in order:\n    hoist/zeta program-head lets, split `ite`/`dite`/match, zeta-unfold fvar program heads,\n    reduce projection heads, and finally apply a registered `@[spec]` theorem.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solve","kind":"def","line":476,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solve","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L476-L565"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.matchFrame?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">matchFrame?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">resourceTy</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">info</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/WPApp.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.WPApp\">WPApp</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Find an unretired `frames` alternative matching the program (earliest source order wins),\nelaborate its frame at the resource type `resourceTy`, and retire it so it applies at most once. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.matchFrame?","kind":"def","line":373,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.matchFrame?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L373-L391"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.stop\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">stop</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">reason</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\">StopReason</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"No further progress possible; emit the current goal as a VC. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.stop","kind":"ctor","line":49,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.stop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L49-L50"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.goals\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">goals</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">scope</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Scope\">Scope</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">subgoals</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Successfully decomposed the goal. These are the subgoals, sharing `scope`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.goals","kind":"ctor","line":47,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.goals","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L47-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The result of one `solve` step of VC generation. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult","kind":"inductive","line":45,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L45-L50"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noSpecFound\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">StopReason</span>.<span class=\"name\">noSpecFound</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e </span><span class=\"fn\">monad</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">thms</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Attr.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.SpecAttr.SpecTheorem\">SpecAttr.SpecTheorem</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\">StopReason</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"No spec was found for the program `e` in `pre ⊑ wp e post epost s₁ ... sₙ`. Candidates\nwere `thms`, but none matched the monad. Reached only when `errorOnMissingSpec` is `false`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noSpecFound","kind":"ctor","line":41,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noSpecFound","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L41-L43"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noProgress\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">StopReason</span>.<span class=\"name\">noProgress</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pre </span><span class=\"fn\">rhs</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\">StopReason</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The target was of the form `pre ⊑ rhs`, but we couldn't make further progress. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noProgress","kind":"ctor","line":39,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noProgress","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L39-L40"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noEntailment\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">StopReason</span>.<span class=\"name\">noEntailment</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">target</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\">StopReason</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The target was not of the form `pre ⊑ rhs`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noEntailment","kind":"ctor","line":37,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.noEntailment","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L37-L38"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.untilPatternMatched\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">StopReason</span>.<span class=\"name\">untilPatternMatched</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\">StopReason</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`until <pat>` matched. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.untilPatternMatched","kind":"ctor","line":35,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.untilPatternMatched","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L35-L36"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.outOfFuel\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">StopReason</span>.<span class=\"name\">outOfFuel</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\">StopReason</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Out of fuel. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.outOfFuel","kind":"ctor","line":33,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason.outOfFuel","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L33-L34"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">StopReason</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The reason why no further VC generation progress is possible on the current goal. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason","kind":"inductive","line":31,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.StopReason","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L31-L43"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Entails","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.RuleCache","Lean.Meta.Sym.InferType","Lean.Meta.Sym.InstantiateMVarsS","Lean.Meta.Sym.InstantiateS"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Solve"}